3.4 Invariant Extractor

This is the crown jewel.

It asks:

What is the minimum semantic skeleton that must survive?

Invariant classes
	•	entity identity invariants
	•	relational invariants
	•	behavioral invariants
	•	procedural invariants
	•	policy/governance invariants
	•	argument invariants
	•	narrative/causal invariants
	•	aesthetic/tone invariants, when declared
	•	safety constraints
