7. Pantheon Daemon Mapping

This architecture plugs directly into the Pantheon.

Spider

Routes artifacts, maps representation topology, notices cross-domain bridges.

Mirror

Checks ethical and interpretive integrity. Prevents ontology smuggling.

Checksum

Verifies provenance, transform lineage, and structural consistency.

Hound

Detects anomalies, silent loss, weak equivalence, broken mappings.

Blacksmith

Proves invariants survived and validates formal transformation contracts.

Darwin’s Sieve

Reality-tests transformed artifacts when empirical claims or executable systems are involved.

Dragonfly

Performs perspective shifts and alternate representation proposals.

Raven

Handles compression and elegant reduction into portable semantic cores.

This is already extremely Pantheon-shaped.

