11. Failure Modes

This needs to be explicit in the repo.

11.1 Surface Equivalence Trap

The target looks right but meaning shifted.

11.2 Ontology Smuggling

The target adds assumptions not licensed by the source.

11.3 Compression Amputation

Too much nuance removed during invariant extraction.

11.4 Rehydration Hallucination

The target invents details to fill gaps.

11.5 Constraint Loss

Critical rules vanish in translation.

11.6 Provenance Break

Output can no longer be traced back to source meaning.

11.7 False Canonization

An inferred transform gets mistaken for a faithful equivalence.

These must be visible, not hidden.

